( Carnage: This shall be my last post until tomorrow dawns.)

** Vlad patted Shesta where he had clutched her fur, remembering how it relieved any pain which might come of his actions but knowing that he hadn't harmed her still. He moved to walk away and return to his quarters when the voice of the woman caught his attention, looking over a shoulder-plate to give visual contact. The fembot he had never laid optics upon before, indicating that she was new to the Iron Fist, alike himself. However, her polite tone was surprising, seeming not to fit in with the surrounding she occupied. He half turned to her and looked her up and down before straightening his posture, Shesta looking at the woman from behind.** " Vlad. Yours?"
